seo: 泛微OA,漏洞检测,远程命令执行,RCE,CNVD-2019-32204
summary: 该插件用于检测泛微OA E-cology系统中的CNVD-2019-32204远程命令执行漏洞，通过发送特定payload验证是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the CNVD-2019-32204 Remote Code Execution vulnerability in the E-cology system of Weaving OA. It verifies the existence of the vulnerability by sending specific payloads.
